{"tid":2063762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［普及Twitter]建構 Twitter社交圈子 邀請朋友 follow你 Twitter！","createTime":"2020-06-14T09:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T05:03:42.000Z","uid":156109,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1acf860c36c75f5842956fe1d9e89c8b370ef565","tid":2063762,"uid":156109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:21:48.000Z","msg":"相信有好多有份打 Twitter戰線嘅朋友喺上面都覺得好孤單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即使起初雄心壯志咁加入 Twitter瘋狂 retweet 同like 但最終都會變咗做做任務心態 上去發吓聲就算<br />\n咁樣其實係唔會長久 <br />\n畢竟 Twitter係一個社交平台 喺上面齋做任冇社交<br />\n你好快就會頹 慢慢就會降低活躍度 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>所以我正式建議喺ig/fb/Snapchat 咩都好 <br />\n貼上自己嘅 Twitter ID邀朋友add你 <br />\n直接帶頭將成個日常社交圈子搬上去<br />\n<br />\n至於資訊吸收方面 一啲本地媒體都可以<br />\n營運埋 Twitter acc <br />\n等啲人可以留喺上面耐啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"0afd7ba432ebffa6468fdf8fd78fdfa0c26b6e7f","tid":2063762,"uid":156109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:22:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63bb7f2c1bf27a494292f86d4cba50275f028ec","tid":2063762,"uid":156109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:22:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e4ca137128c6c8bc20904fbb9b5a36823de984c","tid":2063762,"uid":156109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:23:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"863522b863a6496d50bad1eff3e2e630a17a1428","tid":2063762,"uid":156109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:24:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38c1724bcee4b28b8102e2f5371c9e640c211bb4","tid":2063762,"uid":156109,"like":0,"dislike":0,